 Following the release of his debut EP titled “Girian Update” with notable features like “Igbalode” with Jamopyper, “Deep Down” with Egar Boi, and several hit singles, Estonia based Nigerian artiste/songwriter Scott GiRi comes through (in this season of love and PDA ) with new sophomore EP “Girian Love“, an extension of his debut EP. “Girian Love” serves as his gifts to his fans to tell a tale on the struggles of love with groovy tunes guaranteed to keep fans on their feet. The four-track afro-infused EP boasts a mixture of captivating beats produced by Egar Boi, melodic tunes, and relatable lyrics.  Listen to the EP below: